WEBVTT

00:08:29.518 --> 00:08:31.571
that move on a secondary road network.

00:08:32.024 --> 00:08:33.925
And so without a single stop,

00:08:33.949 --> 00:08:35.536
nor a lengthy transfer,

00:08:35.560 --> 00:08:38.969
you are now sitting in a bus
that is headed toward your suburb.

00:08:39.647 --> 00:08:41.573
And when you get close,

00:08:41.597 --> 00:08:44.904
the section you're sitting in detaches

00:08:44.928 --> 00:08:47.878
and self-drives you
right to your doorstep.

00:08:48.523 --> 00:08:51.184
It is collective and individual
at the same time.

00:08:51.922 --> 00:08:56.799
This could be one of the shared,
modular, driverless vehicles of tomorrow.

00:08:57.681 --> 00:08:58.842
Now ...

00:08:59.217 --> 00:09:02.375
as if walking in a city
buzzing with drones,